250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132560/extras/2ccdd54c26a6b57597e5f86c84ea2122.webm?t=1773702678\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132560/extras/2ccdd54c26a6b57597e5f86c84ea2122.mp4?t=1773702678\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build Relationships</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What’s a vacation without making some new friends? Borgo Marina is filled with locals who are looking to strike up a conversation, play some games, or even looking for something a little bit more than friendship?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132560/extras/a2e027fbbf3778f17666053ade8d9923.poster.avif?t=1773702678\" width=500 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132560/extras/a2e027fbbf3778f17666053ade8d9923.webm?t=1773702678\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132560/extras/a2e027fbbf3778f17666053ade8d9923.mp4?t=1773702678\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>The Cozy Life</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solving puzzling crimes isn’t all you’ll do! After all, you came for a vacation! Kick back and relax solo or with villagers in a variety of fun mini-games around town. Cook some food, go fishing, play marbles on the beach, go swimming, or play at the arcade. If you’re looking to bring in some extra cash, you can also pick up part-time jobs like serving gelato to earn some money for spending. How you spend your vacation is up to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132560/extras/e4841930cc2432dafd2d50db6104886f.poster.avif?t=1773702678\" width=500 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132560/extras/e4841930cc2432dafd2d50db6104886f.webm?t=1773702678\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132560/extras/e4841930cc2432dafd2d50db6104886f.mp4?t=1773702678\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
